"35:3:12" : {s: 35, a: 3, w: 12, r: "رزق", t: "يَرْزُقُكُم", l: "رَزَقَ", lc: 61, tl: "yarzuqukum", lb: "যোগানো, সংস্থান দেওয়া, সরবরাহ করা",e: "who provides for you", b: "তোমাদের রিযক দেয় (যে)", i: "memberi rezki kepadamu", f: 4, rm: "to provide, supply, bestow, grant, means of subsistance. turzaqan - you both shall be supplied. rizq - bounty, gift, portion/share. raziq - one who provides or supplies. razzaq  -great provider/supplier.", ag: "فعل مضارع وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "رِزْقٌۭ"},
